                             'Permutax' 1.3

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Permutax' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you try to clear all game
boards filled with various coloured tiles. The idea is to permutate
2 tiles in such a way that at least one tile match 1 to 4
neighbouring tiles (either on the left, right, upper row or lower
row). When neighbouring tiles match, they are removed from the
board.

  An important advice: just do not isolate tiles!

  Have fun!

